RACE.RACE_TEXT: DELTA DOWNS RACE 1 5F Dirt CR: 39. Maiden Claiming Purse 18000. FOR ACCREDITED LA BRED MAIDENS, FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Claiming Price $10,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CALL ME COLLECT tracked the leader and took the lead at the quarter pole then drew off. CHELSEA'S GLORY chased the leaders from three wide and proved second best. CUSTOM DANCER raced near the back down the backstretch then made a two wide bid at the five sixteenths pole for a late run but was no match for the top two. GLITTER STORM was void of the early speed, made a four wide bid at the five sixteenths pole but couldn't gain on the winner. FIGHTING SOLDIER saved ground to no avail. LAST NATIVE CAT was rushed to a clear lead to the quarter pole and tired, took a bad step at the top of the stretch, fell, lost rider and was vanned off. STEWARDS INQUIRY INTO THE RUNNING OF THE RACE, AFTER A REVIEW NO ACTION WAS TAKEN.
